table_caption: The R2 values (i.e., variance explained) for the training and test datasets for each brain modality. No covariates were added to the model to quantify the variance explained by the brain alone. The R2 as well as the number of children in the analysis and features included are displayed per modality. MID = Monetary Incentive Delay Task; SST = Stop Signal Task; rsfMRI = resting state functional magnetic resonance imaging.
